      <div id="aboutAuthor" class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/author/show/4053574.Chrys_Phillips">About Chrys Phillips</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class='bookAuthorProfile'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__topContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__photoContainer'>
<a href="/author/show/4053574.Chrys_Phillips"><div class='bookAuthorProfile__photo' style='background-image: url(https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1631516726p3/4053574.jpg);'></div>
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__widgetContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__name'>
<a href="/author/show/4053574.Chrys_Phillips">Chrys Phillips
</a></div>
<div class='goodreadsAuthorBadge'></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__followerCount'>
20
followers
</div>

</div>
</div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer10482835764515283832">Australian born writer Chrys Phillips is currently writing the third installment in her Magic Wars Saga, due for release November 2021.<br/><br/>When not writing, Chrys is directing tv shows and movies and traveling the world with her daughter. She is passionate about the arts and her philanthropy and is a self-proclaimed chocolate and movie addict.<br/></span>

</div>
